&lt;li&gt;Develop playlisting strategies and integrated commercial campaigns that support both emerging and established artists.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with marketing, release planning, and other internal teams to align streaming initiatives with broader campaign objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
