&lt;li&gt;A confident communicator and presenter with strong interpersonal skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly collaborative, with the ability to manage complex internal and external relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detail-oriented, organized, and comfortable handling sensitive artist and label information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in Microsoft Office and adept at managing multiple priorities simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
