&lt;li&gt;Support of Product Design &amp;amp; Engineering team and labels’ onboarding of new tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contracts: &amp;nbsp;review / draft data protection provisions in vendor agreements and/or negotiate the longform Data Privacy &amp;amp; InfoSec rider for all of our stakeholders (CMG, GDB, MLive, The Orchard, AWAL, KNT, Ceremony of Roses, PX, B&amp;amp;LA globally…)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;M&amp;amp;A due diligence – multiple deals in progress at once
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;weekly 30 minute all-hands calls (for each deal)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;initial responses review &amp;amp; follow ups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;reviewing data provisions in the sales agreement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;post-acquisition integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orchard / AWAL / KNR – data breach support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data import &amp;amp; export requests – requiring approval or privacy policy interpretation, or a data-share agreement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-OpCo collaborations: location based events – project review; review and/or drafting of contract data privacy provisions (e.g., vendor, location, co-promotion, IP licence agreements), privacy &amp;amp; transparency notices, opt-in language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contest queries – local and multi-market contests - re. data ingestion, sharing data with promoters and prize providers, opt-in wording, UGC advice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Marketing queries - labels, International Marketing and CRM – review campaigns and advise on language, opt-in requirements, transparency concerns, nudge techniques / dark patterns, UGC elements, and incentivising streaming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Subject Access Requests (“DSARs”) – from employees or former employees, artists (increase since Artist Forward), consumers – can take one to three months of to identify, review, redact and collate the response&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CRM – advise on data rights requests (e.g. deletion/unsubscribe requests)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data deletion run twice a year – review each market’s deletion exceptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PX support – DE&amp;amp;I surveys, global career site, company-wide initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Litigation support – nuisance cookie claims, DSARs escalating to litigation

