&lt;p&gt;As Associate Director, Label Analytics, you will be the primary analytics lead for Sony Music Nashville + Provident Label Group, utilizing data to influence strategic decision-making working with executives at the highest levels of Nashville + Provident.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will utilize a range of data sources in generating analyses to evaluate track, album and artist performance, inform release strategies, understand artist audiences, identify growth opportunities, assess campaign performance, share competitive/industry insights, and support the data needs of the labels.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In collaboration with other members of the Insights &amp;amp; Reporting team, you will also be tasked with developing new reports, tools / dashboards + methodologies that adapt with the ever-evolving needs of the industry and leverage ongoing innovation across technology.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
