&lt;li&gt;Lead the execution and presentation of recurring daily + weekly analyses, including release forecasting, consumption reports, industry trends, artist audience reports, and label-specific meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in transitioning existing reports and analyses to new internal platforms + technology partners, including finding ways to drive increased efficiencies with AI.&lt;/li&gt;
